title: DAN MORGENSTERN RECALLS DEXTER GORDON  (July 6, 2018)
description: An affectionate portrait of Dexter by Dan Morgenstern, captured in his Upper West Side apartment on July 6, 2018, by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com).
